{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Garasi Log API",
    "version": "2.0.0",
    "description": "Vehicle maintenance record API. All endpoints require `Authorization: Bearer <API_TOKEN>`.\n\n## Model\n\n`vehicles → visits → line_items`, plus `odometer_logs` (refuels/readings) and `attachments` (receipt photos in R2). **One receipt = one visit.** Visits can carry an optional `label` to group related visits (e.g. one maintenance campaign across several shops).\n\n## Conventions\n\n- Money: full rupiah, integer (`108000`, never `108` or `108.000`)\n- Dates: ISO `yyyy-mm-dd` strings\n- `category` is required on every item: `rutin` | `aksesoris` | `administratif`\n- No silent defaults: missing required fields return `400 {\"error\": \"missing field: <name>\"}`. Exception: `total` is computed as `round(unit_price × qty)` when omitted\n- `due_km` is an **absolute odometer value**, not an interval: \"next oil change in 3000 km\" at odometer 32000 → `due_km: 35000`\n\n## Receipt entry workflow\n\nWhen entering a workshop receipt (photo or text):\n\n1. `GET /api/vehicles` to resolve the vehicle id; ask if the receipt doesn't clearly match one vehicle\n2. Create one visit per receipt: `POST /api/vehicles/{id}/visits` with `date`, `vendor`, `odometer_km` (when known), optional `label` for grouping, and `items`\n3. Normalize prices to full-rupiah integers (\"60rb\" → 60000, \"1,2jt\" → 1200000)\n4. If a next-service interval is mentioned, set `due_date` and/or `due_km` (absolute odometer) on that item\n5. Upload the receipt photo(s): `POST /api/visits/{id}/attachments` (multipart, field `files`)\n6. Confirm the parsed items with the user before posting\n\n## Refuel entry workflow\n\nWhen given odometer + fuel receipt photos: read the odometer km from the dashboard photo and date/liters/total from the receipt, then `POST /api/vehicles/{id}/odometer`. Full-tank refuels make km/l accurate; log a plain odometer reading (no liters/total) anytime to keep reminders fresh.\n\n## Reminders\n\nA checkpoint becomes *due* when `due_date` is within `REMINDER_DAYS_AHEAD` (14) days, or `due_km` is within `REMINDER_KM_AHEAD` (500) km of the vehicle's current odometer (max over visit odometers and the odometer/fuel log). Sold vehicles are excluded. Due checkpoints are sent daily at 05:00 WIB via Telegram.",
    "license": { "name": "MIT", "url": "https://github.com/endymuhardin/vehicle-maintenance/blob/main/LICENSE" }
  },
  "externalDocs": {
    "description": "Source and full documentation",
    "url": "https://github.com/endymuhardin/vehicle-maintenance"
  },
  "servers": [{ "url": "/" }],
  "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
  "tags": [
    { "name": "vehicles" },
    { "name": "visits" },
    { "name": "attachments" },
    { "name": "checkpoints" },
    { "name": "fuel" }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/vehicles": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "List vehicles with summary stats",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "All vehicles, including sold ones",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VehicleSummary" } },
                "example": [
                  { "id": 1, "name": "Corolla Twincam", "status": "active", "latest_km": 180000, "last_date": "2026-01-18", "visit_count": 63, "spend": 58646000 }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "Create a vehicle",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "type": "object", "required": ["name"], "properties": { "name": { "type": "string" } } },
              "example": { "name": "Yamaha NMAX 2026" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Created (status is always `active`)",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 5, "name": "Yamaha NMAX 2026", "status": "active" } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "Vehicle detail with its visits",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Vehicle with visits, newest first",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "id": 4, "name": "Yamaha All New Vixion 2017", "status": "active",
                  "latest_km": 48210, "last_date": "2026-05-25", "visit_count": 4, "spend": 4879500,
                  "visits": [
                    { "id": 76, "vehicle_id": 4, "date": "2026-05-25", "odometer_km": null, "vendor": "Modifikasi Ori Speedshop", "label": "Refurbishment paska beli", "item_count": 5, "total": 600000 }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}/visits": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["visits"],
        "summary": "Create a visit with line items (receipt entry)",
        "description": "The primary endpoint for entering a receipt: one receipt = one visit. `items` is required but may be empty. Use `label` to group related visits (e.g. one maintenance campaign across shops).",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["date", "items"],
                "properties": {
                  "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
                  "odometer_km": { "type": "integer", "description": "Reading at the visit, when known" },
                  "vendor": { "type": "string", "description": "bengkel / toko / samsat" },
                  "label": { "type": "string", "description": "Optional grouping label" },
                  "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" } }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "date": "2026-06-14",
                "odometer_km": 49100,
                "vendor": "Mekar Motor Cibinong",
                "items": [
                  { "description": "Oli mesin Yamalube Sport", "unit_price": 60000, "qty": 1, "category": "rutin", "due_km": 51100, "checkpoint_note": "tiap 2000 km" }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Visit created with items",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 77, "vehicle_id": 4, "date": "2026-06-14", "item_count": 1 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/visits/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["visits"],
        "summary": "Visit detail with line items and attachments",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Visit with full line_items rows and attachment metadata",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VisitDetail" } } }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/visits/{id}/items": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["visits"],
        "summary": "Append line items to an existing visit",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["items"],
                "properties": { "items": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" } } }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Items inserted",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "visit_id": 77, "inserted": 2 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/visits/{id}/attachments": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["attachments"],
        "summary": "Upload receipt photos/documents to a visit",
        "description": "multipart/form-data with one or more files in the `files` field. Accepted: image/* and application/pdf, max 10 MB each. Stored in R2.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["files"],
                "properties": { "files": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string", "format": "binary" } } }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Files stored",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "visit_id": 73, "uploaded": [{ "id": 1, "filename": "IMG_20260604_093107.jpg", "size": 492568 }] } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/attachments/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["attachments"],
        "summary": "Download an attachment (binary)",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "The file, with its original content type" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}/odometer": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["fuel"],
        "summary": "Odometer / fuel log with km/l calculations",
        "description": "Entries newest first. `km_per_liter` is computed per fuel entry against the previous fuel entry (full-tank method). `avg_km_per_liter` spans first to last fill.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Fuel log summary",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FuelSummary" } } }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "tags": ["fuel"],
        "summary": "Log an odometer reading, optionally with refuel data",
        "description": "With `liters` + `total`: a refuel entry (full tank assumed for km/l accuracy). Without both: a plain odometer reading. Providing only one of the two is a 400. Odometer readings feed the reminder engine: a vehicle's current km = max over visit odometers and this log.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["date", "odometer_km"],
                "properties": {
                  "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
                  "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
                  "liters": { "type": "number" },
                  "total": { "type": "integer", "description": "Rupiah paid" },
                  "note": { "type": "string", "description": "e.g. station, fuel type" }
                }
              },
              "example": { "date": "2026-06-04", "odometer_km": 48210, "liters": 8.5, "total": 110500, "note": "Pertamax, Shell Cibinong" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Created entry with computed km/l",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 3, "vehicle_id": 4, "date": "2026-06-04", "odometer_km": 48210, "liters": 8.5, "total": 110500, "note": "Pertamax", "km_per_liter": 44.1, "avg_km_per_liter": 45.2 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/items/{id}/done": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["checkpoints"],
        "summary": "Mark a checkpoint as handled",
        "description": "Removes the item from reminder digests.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Checkpoint marked done",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 195, "checkpoint_done": 1 } } }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/due": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["checkpoints"],
        "summary": "Currently due checkpoints",
        "description": "What the daily Telegram cron would send. `overdue: true` when the date has passed or the odometer has reached `due_km`; otherwise upcoming within the reminder window.",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Due checkpoints on active vehicles",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DueItem" } },
                "example": [
                  { "id": 211, "description": "Yamalube Sport Oil", "due_date": null, "due_km": 48611, "vehicle_id": 4, "vehicle_name": "Yamaha All New Vixion 2017", "latest_km": 48210, "overdue": false }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "bearerAuth": { "type": "http", "scheme": "bearer" }
    },
    "parameters": {
      "Id": { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "integer" } }
    },
    "responses": {
      "BadRequest": {
        "description": "Validation error",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "missing field: category" } } }
      },
      "Unauthorized": {
        "description": "Invalid or missing API token",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "invalid or missing API token" } } }
      },
      "NotFound": {
        "description": "Resource not found",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "vehicle 99 not found" } } }
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "Error": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": { "error": { "type": "string" } }
      },
      "VehicleSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "name": { "type": "string" },
          "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["active", "sold"] },
          "latest_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"], "description": "Max over visit odometers and the odometer log" },
          "last_date": { "type": ["string", "null"], "format": "date" },
          "visit_count": { "type": "integer" },
          "spend": { "type": "integer", "description": "Sum of all line item totals, rupiah" }
        }
      },
      "VisitSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "odometer_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "vendor": { "type": ["string", "null"] },
          "label": { "type": ["string", "null"], "description": "Optional grouping label" },
          "item_count": { "type": "integer" },
          "total": { "type": "integer" }
        }
      },
      "VisitDetail": {
        "allOf": [
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VisitSummary" },
          {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LineItem" } },
              "attachments": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Attachment" } }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "ItemInput": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["description", "unit_price", "qty", "category"],
        "properties": {
          "description": { "type": "string" },
          "unit_price": { "type": "integer", "description": "Full rupiah" },
          "qty": { "type": "number" },
          "total": { "type": "integer", "description": "Defaults to round(unit_price × qty)" },
          "category": { "type": "string", "enum": ["rutin", "aksesoris", "administratif"] },
          "checkpoint_note": { "type": "string", "description": "Free-text service note" },
          "due_date": { "type": "string", "format": "date", "description": "Reminder by date" },
          "due_km": { "type": "integer", "description": "Reminder by ABSOLUTE odometer km, not interval" }
        }
      },
      "LineItem": {
        "allOf": [
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" },
          {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id": { "type": "integer" },
              "visit_id": { "type": "integer" },
              "checkpoint_done": { "type": "integer", "enum": [0, 1] }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "Attachment": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "visit_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "filename": { "type": "string" },
          "content_type": { "type": "string" },
          "size": { "type": "integer" },
          "uploaded_at": { "type": "string" }
        }
      },
      "FuelEntry": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
          "liters": { "type": ["number", "null"] },
          "total": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "note": { "type": ["string", "null"] },
          "km_per_liter": { "type": ["number", "null"], "description": "vs previous fuel entry; null for first fill or plain readings" }
        }
      },
      "FuelSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "entries": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FuelEntry" } },
          "avg_km_per_liter": { "type": ["number", "null"] },
          "total_fuel_cost": { "type": "integer" },
          "total_liters": { "type": "number" }
        }
      },
      "DueItem": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "description": { "type": "string" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_name": { "type": "string" },
          "due_date": { "type": ["string", "null"], "format": "date" },
          "due_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "latest_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "overdue": { "type": "boolean" }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
